Star Wars actor, John Boyega has made his stand  regarding racism known to all, in a tweet stating ‘I hate racists’. I really fucking hate racists. The Nigerian-British in an instagram live video said  “If you’re a fan of me, and you support my work, and you’re racist, and you’re arguing with what I was saying, fuck off, you fucking dickheads.” John Boyega put his whole career on the line for the culture. We salute you💪🏾🤟🏾🔌 pic.twitter.com/t5YoW69KaK Meanwhile Boyega doesn’t seem bothered about his career as long as blacks killings is stopped. 